title: Dallas 10x25 War and Peace.avi
description:
Yes boys and girls: DALLAS is back, and now that the dream is over, its even better than ever!

Pam accuses Cliff of having a revenge obsession against the Ewings; a court rules in the matter of Jamie's 10% share of Ewing Oil; Ray adjusts to life with Jenna and Charlie; Mrs. Scottfield furthers her plot against Ewing Oil; Sue Ellen wants Mandy back at Valentine.

First Aired: 4/3/1987

This episode features a scene in which Mrs.Scotfield and Alfred watch the film reel that was taken by the CIA of J.R. and Calhoun. The film is actually a scene from episode 231 "Bells Are Ringing" which aired earlier in the season.

When Bobby and Ray are trying make up, Ray calls Bobby his "big brother." Ray is the older brother. As the show established in previous episodes, Jock had an affair with Margaret Krebbs when he was away during WWII. At that time the only son he had with Miss Ellie was J.R. This would make Ray even older than Gary Ewing. Ray, talking to Donna, even refers to Bobby as his "baby brother" in "The Second Time Around."
